  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Ark is dedicated to the enrichment of the human spirit through the presentation, preservation and encouragement of folk, roots and ethnic music and related arts. COVID-19 has forced us to temporarily close our doors, but the spirit of music lives on. The Ark continues to fulfill its mission through new livestreaming concerts, virtual youth and educational programs and expanded social media outreach, keeping people connected to music and each other until we can gather together again.</narrative>
  </description>
